{"article_id":"U343uIJ1D7lzIaA2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Key Republican senators voiced doubts over the latest Obamacare repeal bill ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"narrowing its chances of passage before a looming September 30 deadline .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Maine Sen. Susan Collins told CNN","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"that \" it 's very difficult for me to envision a scenario","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"where I would end up voting for this bill. \"","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"Texas Sen. Ted Cruz said Sunday morning","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that \" right now , they don ' t have my vote . \"","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Two Republican senators","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"- Rand Paul","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"( KY )","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"and John McCain","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"( AZ ) -","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"have already announced","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"they will vote \" no \" on the Graham-Cassidy health care bill ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and show little sign","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"of changing their minds .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"This leaves Senate Republicans with no margin of error :","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"A third \" no \" vote would put them shy of the 50 votes","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"necessary","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"to pass the Obamacare repeal plan .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"And there are few Republicans","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"campaigning aggressively in the bill ' s favor ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"aside from its sponsors .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Time , meanwhile , is running short :","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"The Senate faces a September 30 deadline","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"for moving the latest repeal bill .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"After that , the reconciliation rules","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"they plan to use","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to move Graham-Cassidy","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"expire .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"If this bill doesn ' t pass by the end of the week ,","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"then Republicans would likely need to wait until next year","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"to use the reconciliation process again","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"( which allows budget-specific bills to pass with just 50 votes , rather than the 60","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"required","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"to break a filibuster ) .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Senate Republicans have seen their previous attempts at Obamacare repeal fall short by a small number of votes .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"They now risk the same fate with Graham-Cassidy , a bill","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"that cuts federal health spending by an estimated $ 215 billion","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"and targets the largest cuts to states","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that expanded Medicaid .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Graham-Cassidy ' s defunding of the Medicaid expansion ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"coupled with its redistribution of Affordable Care Act funds ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"hasn ' t won over key senators .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"More moderate Republicans worry","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that the Medicaid cuts would hurt their low-income residents ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"while conservative legislators argue","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Graham-Cassidy doesn ' t do enough","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"to repeal Obamacare .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Collins ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"appearing Sunday morning on CNN ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that she feared what the Medicaid cuts would do to her home state of Maine :","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"I 'm concerned about the impact on the Medicaid program ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"which has been on the books for more than 50 years","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"and provides health care to our most vulnerable citizens ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"including disabled children and low-income seniors .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"I 'm concerned about the impact on costs and coverage .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"We already have a problem under the Affordable Care Act with the cost of premiums and deductibles .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"And , finally , I 'm very concerned about the erosion of protections for people with preexisting conditions , like asthma , arthritis , cancer , diabetes , and what it would mean to them .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"One analysis estimates","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"that Maine would lose $ 1 billion in federal funding over the next decade","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"if Graham-Cassidy became law .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"Cruz also expressed reservations about the bill","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"but likely has completely different objections .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Texas would actually gain $ 35 billion over the next decade","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"if Graham-Cassidy passes","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"because it has not expanded Medicaid .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"But he said at a Texas Tribune Festival event Sunday ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"\" Right now , they don ' t have my vote","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and I do n't think","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"they have Mike Lee ' s vote either . \"","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Cruz didn ' t expand on why he or Lee , a Republican senator from Utah , currently opposes Graham-Cassidy .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"But the two are some of the most conservative senators ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"and are likely to share Sen. Paul ' s concerns","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"that the bill doesn ' t do enough","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"to roll back the Affordable Care Act .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"It keeps many of the law ' s taxes intact , for example ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"rather than rolling them back wholesale .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"As Republican senators were criticizing Graham-Cassidy ,","depth":3},{"id":80,"text":"major health groups issued a harsh rebuke of the proposal .","depth":4},{"id":81,"text":"In a rare joint letter , the hospital industry , the insurance industry , and major doctor groups said","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"they \" can not support this proposal \"","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"and predicted","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"it would \" have real consequences on consumers and patients","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"by further destabilizing the individual market ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"cutting Medicaid ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"[ and ] pulling back on protections for pre-existing conditions . \"","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Still , the bill ' s sponsors remain optimistic .","depth":3},{"id":89,"text":"There will be a hearing on the bill Monday afternoon in the Senate Finance Committee","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"and Sen. Cassidy has promised a new version of the bill in the morning .","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"The bill ' s namesakes , Sens . Lindsey Graham","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"( R-SC )","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"and Bill Cassidy","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"( R-LA ) ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"will participate in a CNN debate that evening ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"defending their bill against Sens . Bernie Sanders","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"( I-VT )","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"and Amy Klobuchar","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"( D-MN ) .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"And they continue to argue","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"that key senators","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"- like Lisa Murkowski of Alaska ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"who has also been critical of the plan -","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"remain winnable .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"It appears they will continue to pursue their bill right up to the September 30 deadline .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":211,"left":184,"right":210,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":184,"left":141,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":128,"ri